
/*
* Find the command that add a new local user
*
* To delete, also the home folder (with sudo rights): deluser --remove-home <user_name>
* To delete user and all associated files (with sudo rights): deluser --remove-all-files <user_name>
*/

- To add a normal user (you need sudo rights):
  adduser <user_name>

- To add a system user (you need sudo rights):
  adduser --system <user_name>
